## Video Requirements:
- Format: MP4 (H.264)
- Resolution: 720p or 1080p
- Duration: 2-10 seconds for activities, 10-30 seconds for idle
- Aspect Ratio: 1:1 (square) or 16:9
- File Size: Keep under 5MB per video for web performance